#

Garlic and Herb Beef Meatballs with Honey Glaze

$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

WheatEgg

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

SavoryComfort FoodFamily Meal

Description

Juicy beef meatballs infused with aromatic garlic and herbs, finished with a sweet and sticky honey glaze.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 1 lb
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh Parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Fresh Basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/4 cup, grated
  • Honey: 3 tbsp
  • Soy Sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black Pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
